{"id":79735,"title":"Vivax malaria complicated by myocarditis.","abstract":"Plasmodium infection (mainly p. falciparum) is usually complicated by cerebral malaria, haemolysis, acute kidney injury and respiratory distress. Myocardial involvement is a rare complication of plasmodium infection. We have reported a case of plasmodium infection (p. vivax) complicated by myocarditis.","date":"2014-06-27","categories":"Parasitic Diseases","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24968563","annotations":[{"name":"Myocarditis","weight":0.887664,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Myocarditis"},{"name":"Acute kidney injury","weight":0.829773,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acute_kidney_injury"},{"name":"Hemolysis","weight":0.821773,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hemolysis"},{"name":"Malaria","weight":0.786589,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malaria"},{"name":"Complication (medicine)","weight":0.783378,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complication_(medicine)"},{"name":"Injury","weight":0.733831,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Injury"},{"name":"Infection","weight":0.72904,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infection"},{"name":"Kidney","weight":0.72365,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kidney"},{"name":"Respiratory system","weight":0.665244,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Respiratory_system"},{"name":"Dyspnea","weight":0.639281,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dyspnea"},{"name":"Acute (medicine)","weight":0.493978,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acute_(medicine)"},{"name":"Cardiac muscle","weight":0.47386,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cardiac_muscle"},{"name":"Stress (biology)","weight":0.258217,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stress_(biology)"},{"name":"Cerebrum","weight":0.201782,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cerebrum"},